Rating: 4
Fantastic! I searched multiple sites for a compote and settled on this one and am glad I did. I made it 2 days in advance and the flavors really melded together nicely. I dislike raisins, so used more tart dried cherries, dried blueberries and craisins. Served it as a side dish to a roasted turkey breast, but had left-overs as dessert. Try it-you'll like it!

