Rating: 4
Loved this. It so easy to make and fast. HOWEVER: the recipe does not tell you to REMOVE the cinnamon sticks and good luck trying to fish out those whole cloves. I won't want to bite into one. I used ground cloves instead, 1/8 tsp because I find it a very strong spice.

